@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry / User wants to create account
CreateAccount : do / Fill details
CreateAccount : exit / Account created

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry / User logged in
WatchVideos : do / Watch videos
WatchVideos : exit / Videos watched

state "Upload Videos" as UploadVideos
UploadVideos : entry / User logged in
UploadVideos : do / Upload videos
UploadVideos : exit / Videos uploaded

state "Save Videos" as SaveVideos
SaveVideos : entry / User watching videos
SaveVideos : do / Save videos
SaveVideos : exit / Videos saved

state "View Saved Videos" as ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos : entry / User logged in
ViewSavedVideos : do / View saved videos
ViewSavedVideos : exit / Videos viewed

state "Discussion" as Discussion
Discussion : entry / User logged in
Discussion : do / Enter discussion
Discussion : exit / Discussion entered

[*] --> CreateAccount

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos
WatchVideos --> UploadVideos
UploadVideos --> SaveVideos
SaveVideos --> ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos --> Discussion

Discussion --> [*]

@enduml
